{
  "texts": [
    "For ease of modeling, we take a different approach to quantifying internal and external content.",
    "Instead of splitting sentences into individual details, we aim to instead predict the number of internal words and external words in each sentence.",
    "In our analyses, which we discuss below, we found that the number of words in internal segments is a near-perfect proxy for the number of internal details.",
    "Likewise, we found that the number of words in external segments is a near-perfect proxy for the number of external details.",
    "To establish whether internal word count adequately captures the number of internal details in narratives, we examined the correlation between these two variables across our datasets."
  ]
}